ng.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Stock-image-of-people-dancing-400x266.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Stock-image-of-people-dancing-800x532.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Stock-image-of-people-dancing-696x463.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Stock-image-of-people-dancing-1392x926.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Stock-image-of-people-dancing-1068x711.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3567940" class="wp-caption-text">音乐会上的人群在空中挥舞着手臂。图片来源：Flashpop，来自 GETTY</figcaption></figure><p> 1 月 4 日，即活动结束前一天，国民警卫队发布了驱逐通知。</p><p>去年的“Big Fucking Party”也取得了成功，在格拉纳达的拉佩萨小村庄举行，吸引了超过 5,000 名参加者。该村村长费尔南多·阿尔瓦雷斯出席了活动，他告诉<a href="https://amp.theguardian.com/world/2023/jan/04/six-day-rave-sees-5000-people-descend-on-spanish-village" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a> ，这次活动“组织得非常出色”。</p><p>其他热门新闻是，一名 18 岁女孩最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/teenager-dies-after-falling-ill-at-glasgows-swg3-nightclub-3567322">在格拉斯哥的 SWG3 夜总会生病</a>后死亡。</p><p>这名少年元旦当天在现场，随后身体不适。随后她被送往医院，随后被宣布死亡。她的去世标志着四个月内第三位在参加俱乐部后去世的人。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/local-politician-attends-big-fucking-party-illegal-six-day-rave-in-spanish-desert-3567924">当地政客参加西班牙沙漠中为期六天的非法狂欢“他妈的大派对”一文</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
